messages.content: Also, since I might not see you for a few weeks: I'm trying to raise money for a bicycle race this summer, where the money goes to the Cystic Fibrosis Foundation. My sister got diagnosed with CF last year; she and the rest of us felt compelled to do something, so we started a fundraising team. If you want, you can give money to one of the bicycle riders on our team (it doesn't really matter who because all the money goes to the same place anyway). Or you could sign up to ride; it should be fun. It happens to be in Ann Arbor this year. Here's the website, if you're interested: http://fightcf.cff.org/goto/teamsweatquest
For sure do
Not really sure yet. But I'll let you know

No, I can't wait til Saturday. I guess maybe I'll just let you know next time I'm visiting Ypsi. It might not actually be that long.

Let me know if you wanna hang out in the next couple days. I leave for Indiana Thursday.
